## CLI Usage ðŸ’»

```bash
# Run a script
merilang script.meri
# or use short alias
ml script.meri

# Start REPL (interactive mode)
merilang
ml

# Show version
merilang --version
ml --version

# Show help
merilang --help
ml --help
```

## Development ðŸ› ï¸

### Running Tests

```bash
# Install development dependencies
pip install pytest

# Run all tests
pytest tests/

# Run with coverage
pytest tests/ --cov=MeriLang --cov-report=html

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/test_lexer.py -v
```

